# shadcn UI Usage Guidelines

This project uses **shadcn UI** for all UI elements.

## Initialization

If shadcn UI is not initialized in the project, use the following command:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

## Adding Components

To install a specific shadcn UI component, use the following command format:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>
```

### Example: Installing the Button Component

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```

## Best Practices

- Always use shadcn UI components for any UI elements
- Install components as needed rather than all at once
- Check the shadcn UI documentation for available components: https://ui.shadcn.com/
- Components will be added to the `components/ui` directory after installation
